112
00:13:24.524 --> 00:13:26.355
Sou meio desastrado.

113
00:13:26.442 --> 00:13:27.898
Tome cuidado!

114
00:13:45.378 --> 00:13:47.494
Nossa.

115
00:13:49.382 --> 00:13:51.873
